  "time_ut": 1656930256,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0dd3\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dd4\u0db1\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb\u0daf? \u0db1\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dca\u0daf?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Is the president alive? no",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mr. Naleen Bandara, Member of Parliament of Samagi Jana Balavega said that the country cannot move forward when a president of a country is in hiding, and accordingly, a reference should be made about whether President Gotabaya Rajapaksa is alive or not.",
        "He mentioned this while addressing a question in Parliament today (04th).",
        "Minister Prasanna Ranatunga, the chief organizer of the ruling party, said that while the President performs his duties from the Presidential Palace, he also travels to various places and some security measures have been taken due to the current security situation in the country.",
        "However, although the minister mentioned that the president is going to various places, it is not possible to see him like that, Samagi Jana Balawega MP Mujibar Rahman said.",
        "Mr. Prasanna Ranatunga said that President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa visited the Parliament in the past few days, however the President does not mention his whereabouts to the members of the opposition or the members of the ruling party."
      ],
